1m-beats-12_96m\">fiscal Q3 2025</a> earnings that saw investors bid up its stock by 20% after hours. And even though investors are clearly taking a very bullish view on this story, I'm</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/885294108/image_885294108.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742039-pure-storage-earnings-hyperscaler-deal-isnt-enough-for-36x-forward-fcf", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 17:18:25"}, {"id": "4741654", "title": "2 REITs To Win In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172980445/image_2172980445.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"2025 Real Estate Investment Concept with Gold Coins and House Icon\" data-id=\"2172980445\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"922px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172980445/image_2172980445.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172980445/image_2172980445.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172980445/image_2172980445.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172980445/image_2172980445.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172980445/image_2172980445.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172980445/image_2172980445.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172980445/image_2172980445.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172980445/image_2172980445.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-ca