Gelsinger since</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1670843479/image_1670843479.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741853-intel-dont-expect-the-debacle-to-end-well", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 16:30:00"}, {"id": "4742033", "title": "Cash Is King: Rubrik Is Soon A Real Cash Cow - Strong Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1711863751/image_1711863751.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The iconic Charging Bull of Wall Street in New York city\" data-id=\"1711863751\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1711863751/image_1711863751.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1711863751/image_1711863751.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1711863751/image_1711863751.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1711863751/image_1711863751.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1711863751/image_1711863751.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1711863751/image_1711863751.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1711863751/image_1711863751.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1711863751/image_1711863751.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Teamjackson</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Rubrik \u2013 you just can\u2019t be without it</h2> <p>Rubrik (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RBRK\" title=\"Rubrik, Inc.\">RBRK</a></span>), a company that specializes in Cyber Resilience, is an entrepreneurial company that recently received The Entrepreneurial Company of the Year award from Harvard Business School being the 40</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1711863751/image_1711863751.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742033-cash-is-king-rubrik-is-soon-a-real-cash-cow-strong-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 16:20:56"}, {"id": "4742030", "title": "Why Exxon Mobil Stock Is Still A 'Buy'", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347477692/image_1347477692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Exxon Retail Gas station. ExxonMobil is the World\"s Largest Oil and Gas Company.' data-id=\"1347477692\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347477692/image_1347477692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347477692/image_1347477692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347477692/image_1347477692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347477692/image_1347477692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347477692/image_1347477692.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347477692/image_1347477692.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347477692/image_1347477692.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347477692/image_1347477692.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) cal